entries.title: Will the stock market drop?
entries.text: The volatility for stocks is heating up, but how likely is it that we'll actually get a 40% plus drop as some think? It all depends.

entries.title: Worried About Retiring During a Market Crash?
entries.text: With bonds and stocks selling off side by side, retirees may have a reason to fear their well-diversified portfolios may not prove enough for retirement.
